        public void removeFromHyPeerWeb(Node deleteNode)
        Removes the node from the HyPeerWeb.
        Parameters:

        Pre-condition:

        Post-condition:

      • findLargest

        public Node findLargest()
        This is a greedy algorithm and only guarantees finding the largest node if the HyPeerWeb is also a HyperCube; otherwise this algorithm only guarantees finding an edge node.
        Returns:
        Pre-condition:
        This node is connected to the HyPeerWeb.
        Post-condition:
        Either the cap node (if it exists); otherwise an edge node.

      • addChild

        public void addChild(Node child)
        Adds the given node to the HyPeerWeb.
        Parameters:
        child - The child node of this node.
        Pre-condition:
        The child node has the appropriate webId (webId = N + 1) and the child node is a child of this node.
        Post-condition:
        The child node is connected to the HyPeerWeb, all connections are set, this node's height is correct.
